Description:Combustion Technique (SVar:X:Count$ValidGraveyard Lesson.YouOwn/Plus.2) deals 2+N damage where N is the number of Lesson cards in your graveyard. P0 controls 2 lands, holds Combustion Technique, and has 2 Lesson cards in graveyard (Firebending Lesson + Accumulate Wisdom). P1 controls a Centaur Courser (3/3). Expected: X = 2+2 = 4, so the 3/3 takes 4 damage and dies (4 >= 3 toughness). Before the wave-5 fix, the DealDamageXPaid path would fire instead and deal 0 damage, leaving the 3/3 alive. After the fix, DealDamageDynamic evaluates ValidGraveyard correctly.

